1
00:00:02,330 --> 00:00:04,764
绝不手下留情!
There will be no mercy!

2
00:00:07,102 --> 00:00:10,537
我妹妹的独子正被钉在十字架上!
My sister's only child hanging from a cross!

3
00:00:10,539 --> 00:00:13,006
- 约瑟...  - 我们需要的是结束这一切!
- Joseph...  - We need this to end!

4
00:00:13,008 --> 00:00:15,308
我们要根据我们的法律来管理自己
We must govern ourselves

5
00:00:15,310 --> 00:00:18,712
这样我们将不再受到罗马法律的制裁
so that we are never again subjected to Roman justice.

6
00:00:18,714 --> 00:00:20,947
你一点有用的事也没做
You did nothing of any worth whatsoever.

7
00:00:20,949 --> 00:00:23,250
给安提帕王让路
Make way for King Antipas.

8
00:00:23,252 --> 00:00:26,052
你的地位仰赖于我的认可
Your position is reliant on my endorsement.

9
00:00:26,054 --> 00:00:29,823
约翰 我有着同样贫苦的灵魂
John, I'm poor and sick in my soul.

10
00:00:29,825 --> 00:00:31,892
很高兴现在送给了你们这块地
I'm glad to give you this land.

11
00:00:31,894 --> 00:00:33,260
巴拿巴 再好不过了
Barnabas, it's perfect.

12
00:00:33,262 --> 00:00:35,462
神给我们每个人都有旨意 我应该去传道
God has a purpose for each of us. I'm meant to preach.

13
00:00:35,464 --> 00:00:37,431
耐心点 司提反 时机会到的
Be patient, Stephen. The time will come.

14
00:00:37,433 --> 00:00:40,233
难道耶稣没有在你将他处死而他又复活前说过
And didn't Jesus say, "I will rebuild this temple in three days"

15
00:00:40,235 --> 00:00:42,636
"我能拆毁神的殿"吗?!
before he rose from the death you condemned him to?

16
00:00:42,638 --> 00:00:44,337
让他安静 让他闭嘴
Silence him. Shut him up.

17
00:00:44,339 --> 00:00:46,706
求主耶稣接收我的灵魂
Lord Jesus, receive my spirit.

